These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 10

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, iced-tea, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, writing, dancing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, trance, house, soul
 1. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan soul##3
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is not the fan trance##6
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking iced-tea or the person who's hobby is writing is the fan house, but not both##10
 6. the person drinking iced-tea and the fan gospel have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan house##3
 8. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the fan soul##5
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person drinking lemonade and the fan gospel##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | water | iced-tea   | tea      | lemonade    |
| Hobby         | board-games     | writing | camping | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | house       | gospel | soul         | trance     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, apple, orange, pepper
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, turkish, german, indonesian
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, chinchilla, ferret, hamster
 1. the indian is the person eating pepper or the owner of the hamster is the indian, but not both##10
 2. the german is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
 3. the indian is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
 4. the owner of the ferret and the indian have different parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 6. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the german##3
 8. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3
 9. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating apple##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
11. the indonesian is in an even position##4
12. the indian is the person eating avocado or the indian is the owner of the hamster, but not both##10
13. the person eating avocado is not to the right of the person eating orange##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | pepper | apple    | avocado | orange    |
| Nationality   | german   | indian | turkish  | indonesian |
| Pet           | ferret     | hamster    | goldfish    | chinchilla    |

