.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, water, mirinda, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, carrot, potato, banana
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, russian, pakistani
1. the person eating banana is the german##1
2. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
3. the person eating banana is the pakistani or the person eating banana is the person drinking water, but not both##10
4. the person eating potato is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
5. the russian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
6. the indian is between the person eating asparagus and the german##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade         | mirinda     | water | juice |
| Food          | asparagus | carrot | banana         | potato   |
| Nationality   | russian     | indian   | german       | pakistani   |

