.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, potato, lemon, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, woodworking, singing, camping
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, malaysian, japanese, italian
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the malaysian##1
 2. the spanish is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the spanish##6
 6. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is the japanese or the person who's hobby is camping is the person eating potato, but not both##10
 8. the japanese is the person eating lemon or the japanese is the person who's hobby is woodworking, but not both##10
 9. the italian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is singing and the person eating lemon##7
10. the italian is on the right of the person eating apple##1
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry  | apple   | potato | lemon  |
| Hobby         | dancing     | singing  | woodworking | camping |
| Nationality   | spanish | malaysian | italian  | japanese |

