.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, fanta, 7up
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, zombie, drama, scientific
4 different pets are kept: rat, snake, frog, chinchilla
 1. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the rat is not the person watching zombie movies##6
 3. the owner of the snake is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching family movies##2
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not the person watching scientific movies##6
 5. the owner of the chinchilla and the person watching family movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person drinking milk is the person watching family movies or the person drinking milk is the owner of the rat, but not both##10
 7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
11. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking 7up##7
12. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | milk   | 7up | lemonade | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | zombie    | family   | scientific |
| Pet           | rat    | snake | frog    | chinchilla  |

