 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
 4. the person driving the jet-ski and the italian have different parity positions##9
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 6. the italian is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 7. the polish is on the far right##1
 8. the spanish is somewhere between the person who's hobby is video-games and the german##7
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
10. the italian is between the person driving the helicopter and the spanish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | board-games   | sudoku | video-games  | dancing |
| Nationality   | german  | spanish      | italian | polish |
| Transport     | bike | jet-ski       | taxi    | helicopter   |

