.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-7::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, asparagus, pumpkin, peas
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, journalist, nurse, videographer
4 different pets are kept: snake, ferret, horse, cat
 1. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person eating pumpkin##8
 2. the scientist is between the owner of the snake and the person eating peas##2
 3. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 4. the person eating peas is somewhere between the person eating asparagus and the owner of the ferret##7
 5. the owner of the ferret and the person eating carrot have the same parity positions##9
 6. the journalist is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the nurse is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 8. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 9. the owner of the snake is the scientist or the owner of the snake is the person eating pumpkin, but not both##10
10. the owner of the snake and the journalist have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |       3        |     4      |
| Food   | pumpkin    | carrot     | peas         | asparagus |
| Job    | journalist | scientist    | nurse | videographer    |
| Pet    | snake      | ferret | horse            | cat   |

