The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking, collecting, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, spy, family, comedy
 1. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
 5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
 6. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 9. the person eating nectarine is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8
10. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is collecting or the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating avocado, but not both##10
11. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | nectarine     | avocado     | pear    | lemon  |
| Hobby         | chess | collecting  | hiking | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | family      | comedy | spy | time-travel |

